    "date": "2025-02-07T17:55:06Z",
    "text": "Small Business Flexibility Act\n\nThis bill provides\u00a0statutory authority for the pooling of tips among\u00a0two pools of employees. The first pool consists of employees who\u00a0customarily and regularly receive tips\u00a0(as is permitted under the current statute). The second pool consists of\u00a0(1) employees who\u00a0customarily and regularly receive tips and are paid at least minimum wage, and (2) employees who\u00a0do not customarily and regularly receive tips.\u00a0\u00a0"
  },
